    <div class="info">
      <h1><span>The Tech Scene in</span> <span>Cancun</span></h1>
      <p>
        Cancun is a city on top of the Yucatan Peninsula that hosts a vibrant community of technologists and entrepreneurs. If you ever visit the area we'd be thrilled to meet up and share a drink with you.
      </p> 
    </div>
</section>

<section class="people">
  <div class="col_1 description">
    <h2>Let's meet up</h2>
    <p>
      Cancun concentrates talent thanks to it's services and tourism idustry, it has one of the most connected airports in Mexico; with direct flights to plenty of destinations, it also counts with white sand beaches and beautiful surroundings along with most large city commodities.
    </p>
    <p>
      We are aware that our local ecosystem is small, and that an outsider vantage point is very valuable. We don't want to sell our products, we want to meet up and chat about small or big ideas that might have in mind. 
    </p>
  </div>

